. 2010
</bibRefCitation>
; 
<bibRefCitation id="EFC64B17FF85FFFEFF57FB6EFEACFAE3" author="Haupt" box="[151,357,1272,1297]" pageId="34" pageNumber="35" refString="Haupt, T., Griffiths, C., Robinson, T. &amp; Tonin, A. (2010) Oysters as vectors of marine aliens, with notes on four introduced species associated with oyster farming in South Africa. African Zoology, 45 (1), 52 - 62." type="journal article" year="2010">
